Alembic migration environment for backend service.

Usage:
1. Install deps: py -3.12 -m pip install -r backend/requirements.txt
2. Generate revision: py -3.12 -m alembic -c alembic.ini revision --autogenerate -m "message"
3. Upgrade DB: py -3.12 -m alembic -c alembic.ini upgrade head
4. Downgrade one step: py -3.12 -m alembic -c alembic.ini downgrade -1
